            <h3>Iligan City’s Must Do List</h3>
            <ol>
                <li>1. Visit Maria Cristina Falls, Mimbalot Falls, and Tinago Falls. Drop by the Macaraeg-Macapagal Ancestral House. </li>
                <li>2. Swim at Timoga Swimming Pool.</li>
                <li>3. Eat a City’s variant of Lechon and Buy Cheding’s Peanuts and Suka Pinakurat.</li>
                <li>4. Visit the Iligan City Hall and the Anahaw Amphitheater.</li>
                <li>5. Climb Mt. Agad-agad for a grand view of the city especially at night.</li>
            </ol>
