            <h4>How to get there</h4>
            <p>From Manila, the fastest and most convenient to Iligan City is to take a flight to Cagayan de Oro City, approximately one hour and 20 minutes travel time. From Cebu City, also take a flight to Cagayan De Oro City, approximately for 20 minutes travel time.</p>
            <p>From Cagayan de Oro, take either bus, a taxi or rent a car and travel 89 kilometers to Iligan City. Meanwhile, the City’s public seaport serves passenger ships taking the Iligan-Cebu and Iligan-Manila routes.</p>
